data.description: Indulge in coastal luxury in this exquisite, meticulously renovated waterfront 2-bed, 2-bath condo on Hillsboro Mile! Discover tranquility with hurricane impact glass throughout, ensuring peace of mind. Inside, a private laundry room with a full-size washer & dryer adds convenience to your daily routine. Savor breathtaking intracoastal views from every room, watching boats glide by as you sip your morning coffee. Step outside, and you'll find a private beach access complete with comfortable beach chairs for those lazy, sun-soaked afternoons. This waterfront oasis comes with an array of amenities, including a waterfront pool, gym, clubroom, BBQ grills, & more! Your safety is paramount with 24-hour building security. To top it off, a covered parking spot is included for your convenience.
